{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070220/extras/Gif04.gif?t=1728892204\" /><br><br>Play famous detective Kobayashi in this one-of-a-kind visual novel: Investigate crime scenes, interview suspects and collect clues to get to the bottom of 5 different crime cases that will challenge Kobayashi's skills and delve into a past he has been trying to forget. But be careful: People will try to fool you, and you never know who is really pulling the strings. Your team members will help - or sometimes hinder - you on the way to uncovering the truth, while you collect important clues and evidence to ensure that when you finally face the criminal, he will have no option but to confess!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070220/extras/AllCharaBanner.png?t=1728892204\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070220/extras/KeyFeatures.png?t=1728892204\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u300aInvestigation\u300b</h2>Examine mysterious crime scenes and collect essential clues to reveal what truly happened!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u300aBattle System\u300b</h2>Confront suspects in nerve-racking one-on-one dialogue battles and choose the correct evidence to prove their guilt!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u300aLight Bulb System\u300b</h2>Delve into the depths of Kobayashi's mind to collect secret hints about the case. Use them wisely!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u300aMultipurpose Mobile Phone\u300b</h2>Grab Kobayashi's phone to text characters and discover hidden phone numbers!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070220/extras/Chapters.png?t=1728892204\" /><br>4 chapters featuring different challenging crime cases, each with its own theme and style <br>+ 1 extra chapter back when Kobayashi was in highschool.<br><br>Chapter 1: \u300aMissing Child\u300b<br>Chapter 2: \u300aMidnight Ghost\u300b<br>Chapter 3: \u300aRoom of Revenge\u300b<br>Chapter 4: \u300aTrue Evil\u300b<br>Extra Chapter: \u300aAt the Academy\u300b","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"I am Kobayashi!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070220/d15a5848a26cd2fafc3708518afd4c6a9129d5f9.jpg"},{"name":"Feeling Good","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070220/aed0478f9e4a4e7480ae39d7ad55f894d3eba2fa.jpg"},{"name":"Confusing Case","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070220/40e8619b62f0e460fc708be6e405017f917243e4.jpg"},{"name":"Escape Room","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070220/7f73f3ea76f34740f48941ba56af80582b9bfa3c.jpg"},{"name":"The Revenge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070220/4990d463ca398c7308586a867e920830e3237c54.jpg"},{"name":"Brotherhood","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070220/314d16a0d748c5f341ce2f19b4456ea9c1730597.jpg"},{"name":"My Old Friend","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070220/ba708e6c040142eaf5de8a97a58e52512c946e67.jpg"},{"name":"Memories ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070220/90b005142a4734dbafb2ab7126793f6cea9ea38a.jpg"},{"name":"Achievement Hunter!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070220/cfb1af4e0075d3c7123884dc4dbf67bb5cd3c162.jpg"}],"total":9},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070220/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728892204","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070220/page.bg.jpg?t=1728892204","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070220/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728892204","cap